---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import MemberProfile from "../components/MemberProfile.astro";
import { members } from "../data/members";
---

<BaseLayout title="Members · TBLT-Agent" description="Meet the three researchers behind TBLT-Agent." overlayHeader>
  <section class="members-hero">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Language Learning · Interaction · Human-Centered AI</p>
      <h1>Three perspectives.<br /><span>One shared question.</span></h1>
      <p>How can AI become a better partner in language learning?</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team-intro section-shell">
    <p class="section-index">THE TEAM · 03 MEMBERS</p>
    <div>
      <h2>언어 학습의 이론에서<br />교실의 실제와 AI 설계까지.</h2>
      <p>TBLT-Agent는 응용언어학, 과업 기반 언어교수법, 교육공학을 연결합니다. 서로 다른 전문성을 가진 세 연구자가 AI와 학습자의 상호작용을 이론에 근거해 설계하고, 실제 교실의 언어 학습 문제를 함께 탐구합니다.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="member-list section-shell" aria-label="TBLT-Agent members">
    {members.map((member, index) => <MemberProfile member={member} index={index} />)}
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
